                  "register": "neutral",
                  "usage_note_source": "Uses 'what' to ask about the specific task, not whether it is the full task.",
                  "usage_note_target": "[TRANSLATE]",
                  "audio_normal": "[GENERATE]",
                  "audio_slow": "[GENERATE]"
                },
                {
                  "example_id": "ex_7_002",
                  "text_source": "Is that everything I must do?",
                  "text_target": "[TRANSLATE]",
                  "register": "formal",
                  "usage_note_source": "Replaces 'have to' with 'must'; sounds slightly more formal.",
